title: Rebirth Of The Great God
description: Rebirth Of The Great God The God of Heaven, also known as “Lin Hao Tian”.He is an immortal genius. He was killed jointly for threatening the status of many fairy lords. At the end of the day, he worked hard to break free from the shackles of time and was born again as a boy. This life will certainly be rewritten and returned to the top of the universe.
